parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the "Stabilitrak" and "Power Steering" warning lights illuminate
the vehicle is hard to steer
and the power steering functionality is lost intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to jerk, hesitate, or fail to shift properly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
The stuck ignition key can cause the driver to be stranded, unable to remove the key, and potentially leading to safety risks.
symptoms: Key gets stuck in the ignition

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The power steering and Stabilitrak issues can cause loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
The electrical issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.

The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to become stuck in the ignition, making it difficult or impossible to remove the key, which can lead to safety issues such as being stranded or unable to exit the vehicle.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition
the engine turns off but accessories remain on
the key can still turn the motor off and on but not be removed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to safety issues.
symptoms: The screen jumps around and randomly changes
the system tries to make phone calls
the backup camera turns on while driving
and navigation directions are recited from an earlier trip.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The chafing of the wiring harness can cause electrical issues, leading to safety problems such as loss of power steering, loss of brakes, and engine stalling.
symptoms: the ignition switch won't turn off
and the stabiltrak and trailer brake system warning lights appear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues can cause safety problems such as loss of power steering, loss of brakes, and engine stalling.
symptoms: The vehicle loses all electric dash and radio
the windows do not go up all the way
the horn requires excessive pressure to activate
and the vehicle goes into reduced engine power mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the 4WD system can cause safety issues such as loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle auto-shifts and locks into 4WD
the wheels lock while in a turn
